cloudwatch-official-guide

monitor your aws resources in real time

basic monitoring sends data points to cloudwatch every 5 minutes for a limited number of preselected metrics at no charge

detailed monitoring sends data points to cloudwatch every minutes and allows data aggreation for an additional charge

cloudwatch metrics can be retrieved performing a get request. 

cloudwatch logs agent is available that provides an automated way to send log data to cloudwatch logs for ec2 instances running amazon linux or ubuntu

metrics data is reatined for two weeks by default

need to move logs to persistent storage like s3 or glacier if you want to keep them longer. 